         <c level="series">
            <did><unittitle>Series II: Constructive Course, <unitdate>undated</unitdate>
                    </unittitle>
            </did>
            <scopecontent><p>This series contains a "constructive course" on playwriting that outlines and
                  describes the facets of a dramatic work. Analyses of the various elements of three
                  well-known plays are also included. While not so marked, this course appears to be
                  the work of W.T. (William Thompson) Price, author of <title render="italic">The
                     Technique of the Drama and The Analysis of Play Construction.</title> A letter
                  from Price is also included in this series.</p>
            </scopecontent>
